  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Gift Life to 1000 water starved families in India</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Erratic rainfall, long dry spell, severe water-crisis has made life full of distress and despair for 1000 poor families in Kalahandi. Hunger, malnutrition, crop failure is forcing people to migrate. The project will help to revive defunct traditional water harvesting structures &amp; build new ones ensuring year round availability of water for drinking, household use, irrigation. It will lead to good health, more income, good yield to farmers, ground water recharge &amp; hope for a good LIFE for kids.</narrative>
  </description>
